'''尼古拉斯·斯托勒'''（{{lang-en|Nicholas Stoller}}，{{bd|1976年|3月19日}}）是一位[[英国|英国]]和[[美国|美国]]男编剧及电影导演，尤其擅长[[喜剧片|喜剧片]]。主要导演作品有2008年的《{{le|忘掉負心女|Forgetting Sarah Marshall}}》、2010年的续集《{{le|大明星小跟班 (電影)|Get Him to the Greek|大明星小跟班}}》，以及2014年的《[[邻居大战|邻居大战]]》。

==生平==
斯托勒生于英国[[伦敦|伦敦]]，成长于美国[[迈阿密|迈阿密]]。他母亲 Phyllis 在[[旅行社|旅行社]]工作，父亲 Eric C. Stoller 是一位[[银行|银行]]高管<ref name="wedding">{{Citation | last = Lacher | first = Irene | author-link =  | last2 =  | first2 =  | author2-link =  | title = Francesca Delbanco and Nicholas Stoller | newspaper = The New York Times | pages =  | date = 9 October 2005 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2005/10/09/fashion/weddings/09vows.html | accessdate = 10 April 2008 | archive-date = 2015-04-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150418220823/http://www.nytimes.com/2005/10/09/fashion/weddings/09vows.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。中学时就读于[[新罕布什尔州|新罕布什尔州]]的[[St._Paul's_School_(Concord,_New_Hampshire)|St. Paul's]]<ref name="JJ">{{Citation | last = Pfefferman | first = Naomi | title = Teen angst bring laughs film director won’t ‘Forget’ | newspaper = JewishJournal.com | pages =  | year =  | date = 7 April 2008 | url = http://www.jewishjournal.com/film/article/teen_angst_bring_laughs_film_director_wont_forget_20080418/ | accessdate = 26 May 2010 | archive-date = 2014-05-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140529053756/http://www.jewishjournal.com/film/article/teen_angst_bring_laughs_film_director_wont_forget_20080418 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，后来进入[[哈佛大学|哈佛大学]]，并为学校的喜剧出版物 ''[[Harvard_Lampoon|The Harvard Lampoon]]'' 写作<ref name="wedding"/><ref>"The Dark Side" WHRB radio interview, 2008</ref>。

